====Referenced techniques====

*Place a condenser microphone a foot or more away from the bell and positioned slightly [[On-axis_response|off axis]].<ref>Professional Microphone Techniques.David Miles Huber and Phillip Williams.Page 79. ISBN 0-872886-85-9</ref>
*Al Schmitt is quoted as saying he uses a 67 (Neumann U67) for recording trumpets.He places the microphone 3-4 feet back, keeps the pad on and sets it to omnidirectional. <ref>The Recording Engineers Handbook. Page 104. ISBN 1-93292-900-2</ref>


